<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { width: 80%; margin: 20px auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; }
        .header { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #e74c3c; margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .footer { font-size: 12px; color: #777; margin-top: 30px; text-align: center; }
        .button { background: #e74c3c; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">Reset Your Password</div>
        <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
        <p>We received a request to reset your password. If you didn't make this request, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
        
        <p>To reset your password, click the button below:</p>
        <p style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="{{resetUrl}}" class="button">Reset Password</a>
        </p>
        
        <p>This link will expire in {{expiryTime}}.</p>

        <p>Best regards,<br>The MarketX Team</p>
        
        <div class="footer">
            &copy; {{year}} MarketX Inc. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
